name: Detox
description:
There is nothing more complete than getting rid of human toxicity. We can put up with other people's toxicity and even our own for a while, but there is a limit and when that limit comes it's time to put out every bitter thought you carried inside you and didn't even know. Release plastic thoughts... The world goes, and the plastic stays.
